metadata.name: King Rayan | SABER X N01
metadata.description:
King Rayan | SABER X N01

Saber (セイバー, Seibā), Knight of the Sword (剣の騎士) and Heroic Warrior of the Sword (剣士の英霊), is one of the three Knight-Classes among the seven standard Thief-Classes. 

// Syntax 

Thieves placed within this class are agile and powerful warriors that have mastered every aspect of swordsmanship. 

They will generally have an overwhelming advantage over Caster-Class Thieves who use mage craft as their main offensive ability due to their Magic Resistance Skill.


2833x4000
